column5: Hey folks, we are camping at Grundy Lake his weekend. I brought my boat up. I made the mistake of thinking that motor boats  are allowed!  Being very close to the French we figured we can hit up a section close to Grundy. Anyone know if a launch nearby that will put us on ti some decent fishing? Thanks very much!
On the pickerel right under the hwy at marina head west and watch out for rocks.
Launch at Cedar Village and Marina, the bridge is 20 seconds away. Lots of parking.
Thanks guys.  We will try Cedar Village. Should we head west or east from the launch? We don't have maps of the waters. cheers
Hey check your PMs I sent you some maps.
